name: Red Black Running Shoes
description:
• Sweat Dispersion: excellent sweat dispersion and Anti-Bacterial so that your feet remain dry and comfortable for longer time period 
• Anti-Skid: The shoes sole is designed after specialized r&d for improved performance in slippery conditions 
• Superior shock absorption: having the capacity to absorb the energy of an impact for improved performance and comfort.
 • Stain reduction: Finley shoes are designed such that they feel natural to your feet and become an extended part of it • Other features- Perfect fit, ankle support, arch support, light weight, high-quality construction.
